      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but my doctor is super hard to get ahold of and honestly i feel like a pill for every problem is just not for me. if i just slowly lower my zoloft dose while i start taking the st johns wort, wouldn't that be a safe way to transition? i just want something that feels more organic maybe??",
