      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you about the serotonin thing but people online say if you do a slow enough taper it's fine. if i just drop down to like 25mg of sertraline and start a standard dose of the herb, is there even really that much risk? i'm just trying to avoid the whole chemical feeling, it's really stressing me out. just tell me straight, is it actually lethal or are people just being overly cautious?",
